    "Meanwhile the development of deep generative learning networks has enriched the horizon of DTI prediction from the perspective of ab initio construction.",
    "Researchers have also explored the attention mechanism from different perspectives, including the singlehead, multi-head, joint, and cross-attention mechanism, to find the key points of model construction and the key links of data interpretation.",
    "Common scenarios using the attention mechanism are depicted in Fig. 9.",
    "Our Table 5 chronologically documents a number of deep learning methods, including the author, year of publication, dataset used, methodspecific description, and method characteristics.",
    "As DTI problems are solved in-depth, several directions inevitably step into a bottleneck."
